            li You must hand in Contributions before the respective compo deadline.
            li In case of too few compo entries for one compo (eg. less than three) the party organizers can cancel or combine competitions.
            li By taking part in a competition you agree that we spread your entry (e.g. through scene.org) and that weâ€™re allowed to use it in non-commercial promotions for upcoming editions of Deadline demoparty.
            li We will disqualify entries containing content which violates German law or are unsuitable.
            li If your entry contains commercial material it will be disqualified as well.
            li If you have questions about these rules, contact the organizers at <a href="mailto:contact@demoparty.berlin">contact@demoparty.berlin</a>

